title: Worst Date Wednesday: He Yelled At a 3 Year Old
description: Jessica tells us the story about the time she went to the Titanic exhibit at the Science Museum with another teacher and it all started with him demanding for the teacher discount, then he proceeded to yell at a 3 year old, chased a napkin for 5 minutes, and the last thing he did was so incredibly rude!
